Who benefits rule:
Who benefits from this frame?
Before accepting any dilemma, contract, test, or ‚Äúethical scenario,‚Äù ask: who gains if I treat this frame as real and complete? If the gain flows mainly to authority, extraction systems, or spectators, your first duty is to question or decline the frame, not perform inside it.

###  Trap checklist (3‚Äëof‚Äë5 rule):
> Treat a situation as likely entrapment, not neutral truth, when you see at least three of:  
> - Forced binary (‚Äúonly A or B‚Äù)  
