Energy drain (theft, depletion, fragmentation) ‚Üí downshift to denser band ‚Üí tighter space, lower-version encounters

Energy coherence (rest, resonance, truth) ‚Üí upshift to lighter band ‚Üí more options, higher-version encounters

**Examples across scales:**
- Hit on the head ‚Üí mind contracts, perspective trapped
- Angry person's field ‚Üí their density makes YOUR space harder to navigate
- Better weather in upshifted states ‚Üí not metaphor, observable pattern

**Why this matters:**

Every vote (attention, curiosity, resonance) is also a dimensional positioning vote.

You're not just "choosing good vibes" ‚Äî you're navigating density gradients that determine what's possible in your field.

